{"tid":1061421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱分咗手","createTime":"2019-03-14T11:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T04:54:42.000Z","uid":90638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"116e16421e3786fb870fb389f0b7fa72dcc7c071","tid":1061421,"uid":90638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:31:12.000Z","msg":"心好痛<br />\n但又唔知同邊個講好田<br />\n<br />\n我做錯過改番好<br />\n但即使我用晒所有心機時間陪佢/接送/送野整野俾佢<br />\n佢都係放唔低，都係冇安全感<br />\n<br />\n佢最後都係受唔住離開咗<br />\n但冇怪過我<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以幫佢鬧我"},{"pid":"5ff130313b2eb5c4ad3e6b750e65d07f1349d8e4","tid":1061421,"uid":90638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:33:55.000Z","msg":"大家一定要珍惜身邊個個<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻你覺得佢唔講道理<br />\n呢一刻你想發下脾氣俾佢氹你<br />\n<br />\n下一刻就失去"},{"pid":"4c3fc40e48b827fd85e1704fe7ced1bc4f143f08","tid":1061421,"uid":196459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:34:33.000Z","msg":"有啲野努力左 人地睇到 都無感<br />\n再做落去你就係戇居<br />\n不智"},{"pid":"dfbf9bdabebaa0c525c098f809188557c986f681","tid":1061421,"uid":181905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:35:32.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n<br />\n分咗一個月 但佢已經有新男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3781b86561fa843da5c2d30622d56596699e11c7","tid":1061421,"uid":90638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfbf9bdabebaa0c525c098f809188557c986f681","tid":1061421,"uid":181905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:35:32.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n<br />\n分咗一個月 但佢已經有新男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"咁真係玩完冇機會了..."},{"pid":"90c154f6b80a5ca370310dcb94edcdbbe06e9614","tid":1061421,"uid":223329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfbf9bdabebaa0c525c098f809188557c986f681","tid":106